questions: What is the description of the condition with code {condition_code}?
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX syn: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX snomed: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#snomed:SNOMED-CT> SELECT DISTINCT ?description WHERE {{ ?condition a syn:Condition; syn:code '{condition_code}'^^snomed:; syn:description ?description }}

questions: What is the start date of the condition with code {condition_code}?
